markdownRemark.html: La Cañada is an excellent golf course about 20 minutes from Gibraltar. It is one of the few municipal (owned by the local government) golf courses in the Costa del Sol. The golf course is nice to play. It can be very accommodating but has a number of challenging holes for the lower handicapper. The course is kept in very good condition and the facilities are excellent.

It can be very accommodating but has a number of challenging holes for the lower handicapper. The course is kept in very good condition and the facilities are excellent.
